---

## Most Important Ones For You
```
__pycache__/     ← compiled Python bytecode, never push
tiny_ai_data/    ← generated index files, user creates their own
*.pkl            ← pickle files
*.index          ← FAISS index files
.venv/           ← if you have a virtual env
.pypirc